  22:../../../../DaisyExamples/DaisySP//Source/Filters/fir.h **** /**   @brief FIR Filter implementation, generic and ARM CMSIS DSP based
  23:../../../../DaisyExamples/DaisySP//Source/Filters/fir.h ****  *    @author Alexander Petrov-Savchenko (axp@soft-amp.com)
